Source code for this project is available at https://github.com/jcorpac/animal-trading-cards/

Running the file on a local machine
    python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8080
    The page with the card will be available at http://localhost:8080/card.html.

Run a container from Dockerhub
    docker run -dit -p 8080:80 jcorpac/animal-trading-cards
    The page with the card will be available at http://<docker machine's IP>:8080/card.html.